<p class=3D"ltx_p">In particular, the stochastic process based on the trans=
ition matrix
<math alttext=3D"\Gamma\mathopen{}\mathclose{{\left(t\leftarrow t_{0}}}\rig=
ht)" class=3D"ltx_math_unparsed" display=3D"inline" id=3D"S2.SS1.p5.m6"><se=
