\Gamma\cdots\Gamma</annotation><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-llamap=
un">roman_=CE=93 roman_=CE=93 =E2=8B=AF roman_=CE=93</annotation></semantic=
s></math>,
and the model will also lack specific dynamical laws describing transitions
