<section class=3D"ltx_subsection" id=3D"S3.SS1">
<h3 class=3D"ltx_title ltx_title_subsection">
<span class=3D"ltx_tag ltx_tag_subsection">3.1 </span>The dictionary</h3><b=
utton class=3D"sr-only button" style=3D"display: none;">Report issue for pr=
eceding element</button>
<div class=3D"ltx_para" id=3D"S3.SS1.p1">
<p class=3D"ltx_p">One of the goals of this paper will be to introduce a ne=
