t=3D"normal">=CE=A8</mi><mrow><mi></mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow></m=
row><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">\Psi\mathop=
en{}\mathclose{{\left(t}}\right)</annotation><annotation encoding=3D"applic=
ation/x-llamapun">roman_=CE=A8 start_OPEN end_OPEN start_CLOSE ( italic_t e=
nd_CLOSE )</annotation></semantics></math> is a <em class=3D"ltx_emph ltx_f=
ont_italic">state vector</em>
