lass=3D"ltx_note_outer"><span class=3D"ltx_note_content"><sup class=3D"ltx_=
note_mark">11</sup><span class=3D"ltx_tag ltx_tag_note">11</span>Moreover, =
if <math alttext=3D"\delta t" class=3D"ltx_Math" display=3D"inline" id=3D"f=
ootnote11.m1"><semantics><mrow><mi>=CE=B4</mi><mo lspace=3D"0em" rspace=3D"=
0em">=E2=80=8B</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-t=
ex">\delta t</annotation><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-llamapun">it=
alic_=CE=B4 italic_t</annotation></semantics></math> denotes each discrete =
time step, <math alttext=3D"n" class=3D"ltx_Math" display=3D"inline" id=3D"=
footnote11.m2"><semantics><mi>n</mi><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-t=
ex">n</annotation><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-llamapun">italic_n<=
/annotation></semantics></math> denotes
the integer number of time steps, and <math alttext=3D"t" class=3D"ltx_Math=
