Markov chain. This analysis provides a theoretical explanation for
the ubiquity of Markovian stochastic dynamics in so many real-world
cases, and represents another new result.</p><button class=3D"sr-only butto=
n" style=3D"display: none;">Report issue for preceding element</button>
