otnote20.m1"><semantics><msup><mover accent=3D"true"><mi>A</mi><mo>~</mo></=
mover><mi class=3D"ltx_font_mathcaligraphic">=F0=9D=92=AE</mi></msup><annot=
ation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">\tilde{A}^{\mathcal{S}}</annotation><a=
