d_POSTSUPERSCRIPT</annotation></semantics></math>, with some stochastically=
 evolving underlying configuration.
Moreover, if indeed <math alttext=3D"\tilde{A}^{\mathcal{S}}" class=3D"ltx_=
Math" display=3D"inline" id=3D"S4.SS2.p12.m6"><semantics><msup><mover accen=
t=3D"true"><mi>A</mi><mo>~</mo></mover><mi class=3D"ltx_font_mathcaligraphi=
c">=F0=9D=92=AE</mi></msup><annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">\tild=
